title: leetTest
description: Object that represents a Leet Code Test that source code needs to be generated for.

LEET_ID.description: The integer id for the Leet Code Problem.

LEET_TITLE.description: The string title for the Leet Code Problem.

LEET_DESCRIPTION.description: The string description for the Leet Code Problem.

LEET_CONSTRAINTS.description: The string description for the Leet Code Problem.

LEET_FUNC.description: The name of the function that Leet Code will execute.

LEET_RETURN.description: The return type of the function that Leet Code will execute.

LEET_PARAMS.description: The parameters of the function that Leet Code will execute.
